# StateLayout
Simple way to change your layout state, like loading, empty, error. Strong customizitaion, written by Kotlin.


# Feature
- 对已有布局零侵入，无需修改现有布局
- 支持对Activity, Fragment, View进行状态切换
- 支持自定义每种状态的布局
- 暴露失败状态View点击回调
- 暂时不支持对ConstraintLayout中的View进行状态切换

